  "translations": {
    "en": "So when he dug and reached the well — the well of Ismail — and knew that he had reached the water, he proclaimed Takbir, and Quraysh proclaimed Takbir. And they said: 'O Abu al-Harith! This is our heritage and we have a share in it.' He said to them: 'You did not assist me in digging it. It belongs to me and my children until the end of eternity.'",
